name: deep_codegen_binding_with_bound_unless_condition
section: codegen-binding-mutation
args: p:Bool a:Int b:Int
type: Bool
expect: True
description: with-bound condition must be visible to unless condition codegen.
law: (= (with [x {a} cond {p}] (do (unless cond (set! x {b})) x)) (if {p} {a} {b}))
